'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 69''' is the sixty-ninth issue of the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[June 20]] [[1979]].

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 29|''Star Wars'' (1977) 29]] {{C|Part 3}}
*"The power of Warlock Part 2: The bizarre brain of Barry Bauman"
*"Micronauts Part 9: The macabre Man-Thing!" (Continuation)
*"Tales of the Watcher: What if World War II had been fought in Outer Space? Part 4: The flames of battle!"

